      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, dice the <strong>tomato<span class=\"text-danger\">[es]</span></strong></p><p>Wash the<strong> gem lettuce</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper and shred</p><p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) the <strong>garlic</strong></p>",
