    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> over a high heat</p><p>Once very hot, add the <strong>lean beef mince</strong> and cook for 7-8 min or until crispy, breaking it up with a wooden spoon as you go</p><p>Once crispy, add the <strong>ground cumin</strong> and cook for 2 min further – this is your  <strong>crispy cumin lean beef</strong></p>",
